  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      There are several factors that influence telomere length in patients with cirrhosis, such as
      metabolic derangements and infectious etiologies, The aim of the study is to compare telomere
      length and other parameters related to genetic instability in telomere/ telomerase system, in
      peripheral blood lymphocytes in cirrhosis from different etiologies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
